1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,770
Let me ask you a serious question.

4
00:01:45,090 --> 00:01:46,479
What do you want to do after graduation?

5
00:01:48,050 --> 00:01:48,960
Like Mr Wu,

6
00:01:49,050 --> 00:01:50,200
I'll be a Chinese teacher.

7
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:51,729
I think it's hard for you.

8
00:01:52,170 --> 00:01:53,250
Then I'll be a writer

9
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,450
like He Xiao Shui.

10
00:01:55,330 --> 00:01:56,800
She can write whatever nonsense,

11
00:01:56,890 --> 00:01:58,470
there are still people writing her letters
to praise her!

12
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,350
How can you look down upon others?

13
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:02,130
It's even hard for you
to write a 800-word composition.

14
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,280
Do nothing!

15
00:02:04,450 --> 00:02:05,520
I'll do nothing at all!

16
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,160
I'll muddle along and wait to die.

17
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:11,420
If you do nothing now, when you grow up,
you won't get money nor a happy marriage.

18
00:02:11,490 --> 00:02:12,370
What will you do then?

19
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:14,320
Is it really that bad?

20
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:17,250
I think I'm not that bad.

21
00:02:17,530 --> 00:02:19,010
How could I be so miserable?

22
00:02:20,090 --> 00:02:21,970
I also think you're not that bad.

23
00:02:22,970 --> 00:02:24,520
I don't want to think too much now.

24
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:26,630
I just want to graduate
as soon as possible,

25
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,880
so as to go to find Wu Zhi Xun,

26
00:02:28,970 --> 00:02:30,800
and be with him as a real couple.

27
00:02:31,610 --> 00:02:32,490
Li Qing Tong.

28
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:34,200
In no way should you rely on guys.

29
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:35,680
They will eventually leave you.

30
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,450
We can only depend
on ourselves in the end.

31
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,720
What's wrong with you again?

32
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:43,850
Nothing.

33
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,560
I just hope we can be together forever.

34
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,040
Fan Shui Shui

35
00:02:56,230 --> 00:03:02,200
[Episode 21]
[I'm Sorry My Future Doesn't Have You]

36
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,880
I'm coming, I'm coming!

37
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,280
We came to visit you.

38
00:03:11,370 --> 00:03:12,250
Come on in.

39
00:03:12,570 --> 00:03:14,360
It's so sweet of you to bring gifts.

40
00:03:14,450 --> 00:03:15,240
Auntie.

41
00:03:15,330 --> 00:03:16,280
Li.

42
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,280
Yu Fen is here.

43
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,520
-Hello, Uncle and Aunt.
-Hello.

44
00:03:18,610 --> 00:03:19,520
Hello, Uncle and Aunt.

45
00:03:19,610 --> 00:03:20,360
Take a seat.

46
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,370
Sit down please.

47
00:03:24,210 --> 00:03:25,090
Take a seat.

48
00:03:25,329 --> 00:03:26,210
Hi, Du.

49
00:03:26,730 --> 00:03:27,470
Uncle.

50
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,440
I slept for a while.

51
00:03:28,970 --> 00:03:30,690
How're things going from your side?

52
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,480
Nothing special.

53
00:03:32,570 --> 00:03:33,840
We're just doing business there,

54
00:03:33,930 --> 00:03:35,530
adapting to changes.

55
00:03:36,090 --> 00:03:36,760
That's true.

56
00:03:36,850 --> 00:03:38,329
Kids are going to college, anyway.

57
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,840
We're finally dismissed
from parental duty.

58
00:03:39,930 --> 00:03:40,960
It's time to do something we desire.

59
00:03:41,050 --> 00:03:42,920
Your husband really has guts.

60
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,490
Doing business really needs courage.

61
00:03:46,010 --> 00:03:46,890
Li.

62
00:03:47,130 --> 00:03:48,880
Come with me to do business together.

63
00:03:48,970 --> 00:03:50,480
Don't do physical work anymore.

64
00:03:52,970 --> 00:03:53,850
Don't mention it.

65
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,520
-Drink water.
-Yeah, okay.

66
00:03:55,610 --> 00:03:56,520
Drink water, Yu Fen.

67
00:03:58,650 --> 00:04:00,320
Well, when will you depart?

68
00:04:00,410 --> 00:04:02,280
-Tomorrow.
-Tomorrow?

69
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:02,760
Li Qing Tong.

70
00:04:02,850 --> 00:04:03,730
Well, how about seeing them off?

71
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:04,520
Sure.

72
00:04:04,610 --> 00:04:05,730
We'll make dumplings tonight.

73
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,240
Li Qing Tong.

74
00:04:11,730 --> 00:04:12,610
That day...

75
00:04:15,410 --> 00:04:16,430
That day,

76
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,890
I drank too much.

77
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:20,450
Forget what I said.

78
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,720
I've never taken what you said seriously.

79
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,880
You...

80
00:04:33,970 --> 00:04:36,670
You really scared me.
I thought you were really mad.

81
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,520
You think I don't know you?

82
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,930
I was a little bit embarrassed that day.

83
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,360
If you move out of the town,
you'll never come back, right?

84
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,570
We've sold out our house.

85
00:04:51,250 --> 00:04:53,890
Maybe we'll never come back
even for holiday.

86
00:04:59,050 --> 00:04:59,960
It's alright.

87
00:05:00,050 --> 00:05:01,520
I'll visit you in the South in the future.

88
00:05:01,910 --> 00:05:02,800
Sure.

89
00:05:02,890 --> 00:05:04,240
Both of you should come.

90
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:06,150
I'll treat you with seafood,

91
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,290
and bring you to watch the sea.

92
00:05:07,770 --> 00:05:08,920
Fine. We'll surely go there.

93
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,640
Stop talking nonsense.

94
00:05:10,730 --> 00:05:12,490
Grab some food for us right now.

95
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:14,370
So easy.

96
00:05:22,170 --> 00:05:23,050
Stop laughing.

97
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:28,440
Let me tell you,
even Shui Shui is able to get out of here.

98
00:05:28,530 --> 00:05:29,480
Impossible.

99
00:05:29,570 --> 00:05:30,850
How can I be fatter than her...

100
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:35,000
Give me a hand, okay?

101
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,760
When we can see Egg Wang again

102
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,080
is unknown to us all.

103
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:50,480
Little by little, we end up separating
from each other.

104
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,090
You'll see them again, sooner or later.

105
00:05:57,490 --> 00:06:00,600
Fan Shui Shui also said
she won't be here next vacation.

106
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,530
Do you think our Tattered Group

107
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:06,440
has no way to be reunited forever?

108
00:06:08,490 --> 00:06:10,160
That's how we grow up.

109
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,850
Will you also leave me eventually?

110
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:17,810
Don't worry.

111
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,800
No matter where I go,

112
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:21,330
we won't be separated.

113
00:06:23,770 --> 00:06:25,850
What if Duan Xiao takes you away?

114
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,320
Li Qing Tong

115
00:06:33,570 --> 00:06:35,040
Could you please do me a favour?

116
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,930
Thank you. No more servings.

117
00:06:48,409 --> 00:06:49,800
I don't see any good about
these smoked, barbecued food.

118
00:06:50,210 --> 00:06:51,480
Why do we have to eat here?

119
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,920
Why not make something to eat at home?

120
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,040
It would be cleaner. Unbelievable...

121
00:06:55,130 --> 00:06:56,130
No, no, no.

122
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:58,280
It's not easy for our family
to eat outside.

123
00:06:59,650 --> 00:07:00,530
Just enjoy.

124
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,600
Okay.

125
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,560
My daughter...

126
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,080
is... is right.

127
00:07:05,010 --> 00:07:06,200
Our family

128
00:07:06,690 --> 00:07:08,280
hasn't eaten outside for a long time.

129
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,200
Help yourself with some.

130
00:07:14,410 --> 00:07:15,810
Drink some water.
It'll make you feel better.

131
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:23,480
Coming.

132
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:28,930
Come on in.

133
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,150
You are at home alone?

134
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:34,790
Where are the others?

135
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,370
They had some invitations.

136
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:40,130
Have a seat.

137
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,200
You cooked it?

138
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,200
Have a try.

139
00:07:57,930 --> 00:07:58,810
Tastes so good.

140
00:08:07,850 --> 00:08:08,730
Why don't you eat?

141
00:08:09,490 --> 00:08:10,870
I made it specially for you.

142
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,840
I'm not hungry.

143
00:08:13,450 --> 00:08:14,480
What happened to you?

144
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,280
Why this all of a sudden?

145
00:08:17,890 --> 00:08:18,770
Nothing.

146
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:20,360
I just wanted to cook for you.

147
00:08:20,850 --> 00:08:21,730
Well...

148
00:08:21,850 --> 00:08:23,130
In TV dramas,

149
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:25,450
they do the same thing
if they like someone.

150
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,920
What did you say?

151
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,920
Like someone.

152
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,080
Like whom?

153
00:08:30,170 --> 00:08:31,050
Like you.

154
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,760
I just feel that

155
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:37,130
I've never made a meal for you.

156
00:08:37,690 --> 00:08:38,510
Besides,

157
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:41,280
there are so many things
we haven't done together.

158
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,230
No matter what you want to do
in the future,

159
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,250
I'll do it with you if I can.

160
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,130
You are not being yourself today.

161
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,970
Do... Do you feel happy if I shout at you?

162
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:53,410
No.

163
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,840
I hope you can keep your attitude just now

164
00:08:54,930 --> 00:08:56,200
for a longer time.

165
00:08:56,290 --> 00:08:57,870
-Just a while.
-No, I won't do it. I can't.

166
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,400
You've done eating.
I'll keep it to myself.

167
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,070
No, no. I...

168
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,080
I'm not done yet.

169
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,040
It's so delicious.

170
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:09,920
Coriander is also fine.

171
00:09:10,010 --> 00:09:10,890
Have some coriander.

172
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,360
Even coriander is delicious.

173
00:09:15,290 --> 00:09:16,410
What a psycho.

174
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,640
Duan Xiao.

175
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,720
If one day,

176
00:09:22,810 --> 00:09:25,210
I suddenly leave like Egg Wang,

177
00:09:26,530 --> 00:09:27,520
will you miss me?

178
00:09:27,610 --> 00:09:28,790
Why would I miss you?

179
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:30,130
I'll be with you wherever you go.

180
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,360
Fine.

181
00:09:35,410 --> 00:09:38,200
Can I have my meals cooked
by you every day in the future?

182
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:39,240
No way.

183
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,520
Go quickly.

184
00:09:43,370 --> 00:09:44,890
Can you give me a kiss?

185
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:48,840
I'll go now.

186
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:49,800
Bye-bye.

187
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,200
Bye-bye.

188
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:08,090
Time to check the tickets.

189
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:18,890
You have to go in, don't you?

190
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,120
Don't worry.

191
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:21,330
I'll stay with you for a while.

192
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:33,880
[Pipi Lu Collection]

193
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:34,970
This is for you.

194
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:39,400
How come you still remember this book.

195
00:10:41,090 --> 00:10:42,280
That day, actually,

196
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,590
We didn't bump into each other.

197
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:46,170
I went to see you on purpose.

198
00:10:46,730 --> 00:10:47,610
I know.

199
00:10:52,530 --> 00:10:54,600
We're about to stop checking tickets.

200
00:10:58,180 --> 00:10:58,970
Go now.

201
00:10:59,050 --> 00:11:00,050
We're about to stop checking tickets.

202
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:04,970
We're about to stop checking tickets.

203
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:07,700
[Beijing]

204
00:11:08,730 --> 00:11:09,610
I'm leaving.

205
00:11:11,250 --> 00:11:12,570
Have a safe trip.

206
00:11:23,670 --> 00:11:26,110
[Tieyuan Station]

207
00:11:30,730 --> 00:11:32,080
Take good care of yourself.

208
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,160
[Tieyuan Station]

209
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:57,520
[Pipi Lu Collection]

210
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:02,840
Do you still remember
the first time we ate together?

211
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:03,880
What we ate was this.

212
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:05,640
Of course I remember.

213
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:07,440
This is the most
delicious stew in the world.

214
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,840
Eat more then.

215
00:12:12,010 --> 00:12:14,440
Actually, I had no money that day.

216
00:12:14,530 --> 00:12:16,440
I didn't pay it until several days later.

217
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:22,530
Duan Xiao.

218
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,910
Let me ask you something.

219
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,120
Answer honestly.

220
00:12:28,690 --> 00:12:31,190
What are you going to do after graduation?

221
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,330
Find a job.

222
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,880
Then,

223
00:12:33,970 --> 00:12:35,210
we'll live together.

224
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,440
But,

225
00:12:39,810 --> 00:12:41,600
what if I'm leaving?

226
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:43,120
What if I'll go abroad?

227
00:12:43,210 --> 00:12:44,090
Wherever you go,

228
00:12:44,450 --> 00:12:45,330
I'll be with you.

229
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,640
What happened to you?

230
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,770
You look so odd today.

231
00:12:56,210 --> 00:12:57,090
I'm fine.

232
00:12:57,650 --> 00:12:58,470
I'm fine.

233
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,910
Don't be lost in conjunctures.

234
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,170
Eat. Eat more.

235
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,130
Well, how about singing a song for me?

236
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,200
Sure.

237
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:23,640
♫ Open the window,
the world is different outside ♫

238
00:13:23,730 --> 00:13:26,920
♫ Winter's full of birds and fragrance ♫

239
00:13:27,010 --> 00:13:31,160
♫ Summer's snow is all in white ♫

240
00:13:50,410 --> 00:13:54,780
[No. 1 Students' Dormitory]

241
00:13:57,090 --> 00:13:59,250
Wu Zhi Xun called you just now.

242
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,720
The supermarket in our college

243
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,280
really has
recruitment advertisement posted

244
00:14:30,370 --> 00:14:31,760
It reads like this:

245
00:14:31,850 --> 00:14:33,680
"We support students
to work for studying."

246
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:34,890
Let's have a try.

247
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:36,570
Why should we work?

248
00:14:37,210 --> 00:14:38,880
Because we are college students,

249
00:14:38,970 --> 00:14:40,790
we should share the burden
with our family.

250
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:43,000
I don't want my parents
to work so hard anymore.

251
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,450
You're right.

252
00:14:45,770 --> 00:14:48,160
And I also want to save some money.

253
00:14:48,770 --> 00:14:50,520
I want to buy a mobile phone,

254
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,840
so that I can contact
Wu Zhi Xun at any time.

255
00:14:52,930 --> 00:14:54,850
You're doing it for a man, after all.

256
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:57,690
Then what should I do?

257
00:14:58,280 --> 00:14:59,200
I'm unlike you.

258
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:01,480
You have Duan Xiao always
following you as if he were your tail.

259
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:03,880
So what?

260
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:05,250
It won't last long.

261
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,600
I want to tell everyone some good news.

262
00:15:22,650 --> 00:15:24,850
My boyfriend is treating everyone a meal
tomorrow.

263
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,760
When did your boyfriend
become so generous?

264
00:15:27,850 --> 00:15:29,800
Last time he wasn't even willing
to buy us a bottle of water.

265
00:15:29,890 --> 00:15:31,130
So I changed boyfriend.

266
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:32,880
You changed again?

267
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:34,240
And this one

268
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:35,970
is known to you all.

269
00:15:36,970 --> 00:15:37,850
Who is him?

270
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,930
Fang Jin Han.

271
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:41,570
What?

272
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:43,370
Surprised?

273
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:46,240
He was always badgering Li Jin Bu before.

274
00:15:46,330 --> 00:15:47,240
Stop talking nonsense.

275
00:15:47,330 --> 00:15:48,440
We're not friends.

276
00:15:48,850 --> 00:15:50,550
Anyway,

277
00:15:50,640 --> 00:15:51,840
I got him.

278
00:15:52,610 --> 00:15:53,720
It can be regarded

279
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:55,800
as a happy ending.

280
00:15:56,450 --> 00:15:58,200
Get along with him well.

281
00:15:58,290 --> 00:15:59,910
Don't change another one before long.

282
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,930
You bet.

283
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,720
I've made up my mind.

284
00:16:02,810 --> 00:16:04,120
I'm serious about this.

285
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,210
We won't separate until graduation.

286
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:06,360
Xiao Shui.

287
00:16:06,450 --> 00:16:07,270
We're going to graduate.

288
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,760
Why haven't you got a boyfriend?

289
00:16:08,850 --> 00:16:10,120
I've got one already.

290
00:16:10,490 --> 00:16:11,440
What?

291
00:16:11,850 --> 00:16:12,760
Who is him?

292
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:13,870
One of my folks in my hometown.

293
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:14,840
His name is Da Wang.

294
00:16:15,330 --> 00:16:17,360
When did you get this boyfriend?

295
00:16:18,570 --> 00:16:19,590
Why didn't you tell us?

296
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:21,760
How did that happen?
When did he confess his love to you?

297
00:16:22,410 --> 00:16:23,850
He told me last night.

298
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,560
There's nothing to talk about.

299
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:27,120
Since he's expressed his feelings,

300
00:16:27,210 --> 00:16:28,690
how could I refuse him?

301
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:32,120
How can you remain so calm.

302
00:16:32,530 --> 00:16:35,480
It seems like a plain meal for you.

303
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:37,080
Exactly. He expressed
his affection while eating.

304
00:16:37,170 --> 00:16:38,050
What the heck.

305
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:40,440
What kind of people
are there in my dormitory.

306
00:16:40,530 --> 00:16:41,520
I'm overwhelmed.

307
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,470
I won't talk to you.
I'm going to see Da Wang.

308
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:44,440
Bye-bye.

309
00:16:45,370 --> 00:16:47,000
I'll go to see Fang Jin Han.

310
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:50,840
Okay. Go away.

311
00:16:51,210 --> 00:16:53,240
Don't come back tonight if you dare.

312
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:58,360
Hello.

313
00:16:58,440 --> 00:16:59,320
[Qing Tong.]

314
00:17:00,370 --> 00:17:02,270
Why are you calling me so late?

315
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,800
I'm so pissed off tonight.

316
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:04,770
[What happened?]

317
00:17:05,970 --> 00:17:08,079
All of them are showing off
their boyfriends in front of me.

318
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,930
They tease me
for not having a boyfriend around.

319
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,920
[It's not a big deal.]

320
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,359
Not a big deal?

321
00:17:15,450 --> 00:17:16,400
[It's okay.]

322
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,599
[When I come back,]

323
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,119
[we'll also make them jealous.]

324
00:17:19,369 --> 00:17:20,250
Okay.

325
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:21,960
[Qing Tong.]

326
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:23,760
[I have to hang up.]

327
00:17:23,839 --> 00:17:26,290
[I have a very important project
to prepare tonight.]

328
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:27,480
[I'll hang up now.]

329
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,000
[Take good care of yourself.]

330
00:17:29,090 --> 00:17:30,320
[Go to bed earlier.]

331
00:17:30,410 --> 00:17:31,290
[Good night.]

332
00:17:32,930 --> 00:17:33,810
Good night.

333
00:17:40,050 --> 00:17:41,600
Waiting for three hours every night,

334
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,490
for just two-minute chat in average.

335
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,710
Ms Li,

336
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,750
are you tired or not?

337
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:48,570
He's busy today.

338
00:17:48,970 --> 00:17:50,530
He's not like this every day.

339
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,200
Look how pathetic you are.

340
00:17:53,290 --> 00:17:54,490
Forget it.

341
00:17:56,780 --> 00:17:58,760
[No. 2 Dining Hall]

342
00:17:58,770 --> 00:17:59,760
Are you sure

343
00:17:59,850 --> 00:18:01,880
you can do physical work?

344
00:18:03,530 --> 00:18:04,480
No problem.

345
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:06,400
Well, we're from a poor family.

346
00:18:06,490 --> 00:18:07,890
We grew up doing tiring work.

347
00:18:08,210 --> 00:18:09,400
We're so robust.

348
00:18:10,430 --> 00:18:12,620
Fine. Let's talk about
the unpleasant things first.

349
00:18:12,760 --> 00:18:14,040
You really have to work hard.

350
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:15,720
I didn't intend to recruit girls.

351
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:17,120
If you don't do it well,

352
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,240
I'll change you at any time.

353
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:19,070
Please be assured.

354
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,160
We can do it.

355
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,410
I can't do it.

356
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,560
I can't move them anymore.

357
00:18:25,650 --> 00:18:27,610
Who said there would be
no problem just now?

358
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,430
Fine. Take a rest. I'll do it.

359
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:30,360
Why?

360
00:18:30,450 --> 00:18:31,650
Why aren't you tired?

361
00:18:32,450 --> 00:18:34,080
I regard Wu Zhi Xun as a good model.

362
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,290
I can't be so fragile.

363
00:18:35,970 --> 00:18:37,320
Take a rest. I'll move them.

364
00:18:52,690 --> 00:18:53,770
Li Jin Bu

365
00:18:54,570 --> 00:18:55,770
Long time no see.

366
00:18:56,850 --> 00:18:57,800
Long time no see.

367
00:18:58,120 --> 00:19:00,810
Why haven't you participated
in the drama club activities recently?

368
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:03,960
Recently I've been taking
a part-time job to earn money.

369
00:19:05,210 --> 00:19:06,090
Pretty good.

370
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:08,120
Do you know

371
00:19:08,210 --> 00:19:10,050
I'm going out with Zhang Wan Wan?

372
00:19:10,410 --> 00:19:11,290
I know.

373
00:19:12,760 --> 00:19:14,200
Actually, I...

374
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:16,120
You should understand me.

375
00:19:16,710 --> 00:19:18,240
-I was...
-No, no, no.

376
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:21,040
Stop talking inappropriate stuff.

377
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:23,320
We're not for each other anyhow.

378
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:25,630
I got it.

379
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:28,950
You're a really strange person.

380
00:19:29,590 --> 00:19:31,000
You're so hard to approach.

381
00:19:31,790 --> 00:19:34,320
It's so wise of me to give you up.

382
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:38,390
This is for you.

383
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:39,440
I'm leaving now.

384
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:40,830
See you later.

385
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:41,800
Bye-bye.

386
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,440
You, you...

387
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:07,640
Why did you come here?

388
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:11,440
I can't buy anything in my own school?

389
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:19,760
You two get along well?

390
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,390
Which two?

391
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:26,630
Which two?

392
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:28,440
You and the Swift Leg?

393
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:30,430
Of course you and Four-Eyes.

394
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:40,640
You've decided
not to talk to me again, right?

395
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,240
I have not.

396
00:20:44,950 --> 00:20:45,830
Fine.

397
00:20:46,710 --> 00:20:49,150
When Four-Eyes comes to our college,

398
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,400
I'll treat both of you a dinner.

399
00:20:54,870 --> 00:20:56,000
We're friends.

400
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:00,400
Okay.

401
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,480
I want to eat Northeast dishes.

402
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:06,720
I'm back.

403
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:12,840
Why did you two change bed?

404
00:21:13,670 --> 00:21:15,160
I'm so tired.

405
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:18,150
I feel so tired.

406
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,680
Working people are so great.

407
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:24,760
I just want to lie in bed
after everyday work.

408
00:21:25,350 --> 00:21:27,110
Who has strength to make a phone call?

409
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,630
[Once activities are finished,]

410
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:30,000
[I'll go see you immediately.]

411
00:21:30,390 --> 00:21:31,270
Okay.

412
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:33,520
[You sound a little bit perfunctory.]

413
00:21:35,520 --> 00:21:36,480
Okay.

414
00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:37,920
[Now you're talking.]

415
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:39,520
[I'll hang up now.]

416
00:21:39,780 --> 00:21:41,000
-[Good night.]
-Good night.

417
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:42,600
-[Miss you...]
-Miss you.

418
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,560
Good night. Miss you.

419
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:59,200
[Lin Yang Teachers College]
[Preschool Education]

420
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,190
Come on. Have lunch.

421
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,830
I won't go. You go first.

422
00:22:07,280 --> 00:22:09,760
How have you suddenly
become obsessed with learning?

423
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,870
I'm unlucky in love,

424
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,630
I should find other things to do.

425
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:17,110
If you like her,
you should keep chasing her.

426
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,950
She just has a boyfriend.

427
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:20,600
She hasn't got married yet.

428
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,400
What are you talking about?

429
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,000
We're all friends.

430
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:49,230
Excuse me, sir.

431
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:50,200
Coming.

432
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:51,590
What's the matter?

433
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,910
Please help me find out
why I can't see the image.

434
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,560
Here we go.

435
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:05,320
Can you see me?

436
00:23:07,430 --> 00:23:08,310
Yes, I can.

437
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:13,480
Why the image is gone again?

438
00:23:14,590 --> 00:23:16,790
Excuse-me, it's not working again.

439
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:18,550
Wait a moment. I'm busy.

440
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:24,150
Hurry up.

441
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,880
I'm in a hurry.

442
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,960
Shut up. So noisy.

443
00:23:34,270 --> 00:23:35,480
What are you doing here?

444
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:38,600
I'm surfing the Internet.

445
00:23:39,110 --> 00:23:40,160
Where's the video gone?

446
00:23:52,990 --> 00:23:53,670
Do you...

447
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,760
Do you know how to handle the camera?

448
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,030
I don't know why

449
00:23:58,120 --> 00:23:59,400
I can't see anything.

450
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:25,840
Can you see me?

451
00:24:26,840 --> 00:24:28,880
[Are you Chen Jun He?]

452
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:30,710
Four-Eyes.

453
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:31,920
You're still alive.

454
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,900
Well, when will you come to our school?

455
00:24:35,990 --> 00:24:37,600
I'll treat you two a dinner.

456
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:40,600
Da Fan.

457
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,150
Da Fan.

458
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:44,320
Let's go.

459
00:24:55,150 --> 00:24:56,870
[Don't be with him if not necessary.]

460
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:57,840
[Okay?]

461
00:24:58,600 --> 00:25:00,150
I'm not with him.

462
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:02,000
It's just a coincidence.

463
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:03,800
When I'm not there,

464
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:05,710
does he always bother you?

465
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:07,110
It's impossible.

466
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,950
He already knows we're together.

467
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,390
[That's why]

468
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:12,520
he thinks he's got a chance.

469
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:13,790
I'm just...

470
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,550
He helped me as he happened to be around.

471
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:17,680
Stop making up stories?

472
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,600
Li Qing Tong.

473
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:21,630
You're in the same college,

474
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,840
but I'm not.

475
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,600
It's normal for me to worry about it.

476
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:26,680
[Wait.]

477
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:29,550
So, so you think I'm unreliable, right?

478
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,960
[Of course you're reliable,]

479
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:32,400
but he's not.

480
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:37,620
Do you hope

481
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:39,910
that we should never talk to each other?

482
00:25:40,470 --> 00:25:41,640
[I didn't say that.]

483
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:44,360
I also don't want to interfere
with your freedom.

484
00:25:44,990 --> 00:25:46,750
What on earth do you want me to do?

485
00:25:46,840 --> 00:25:48,390
Just say it.

486
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:50,760
Nothing.

487
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:53,640
Forget it.

488
00:25:54,670 --> 00:25:56,800
It seems you have nothing else to say.

489
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:01,360
Why don't you just keep reading books?

490
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:03,200
I'll log off.

491
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:20,990
[Cambridge IELTS
Previous Exams' Explanation]

492
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:38,790
Mum.

493
00:26:39,110 --> 00:26:41,750
[Your dad asked you to meet Professor He]

494
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:44,200
[to get the chance of being an exchange
student as soon as possible.]

495
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,550
It's useless.

496
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:48,560
Those chances can't be gained
with connections.

497
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:50,160
[What are you talking about?]

498
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:52,950
[He and your dad have been
university classmates for years.]

499
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:55,110
[And now he's in the same college as you.]

500
00:26:55,190 --> 00:26:57,000
[What's wrong with visiting him?]

501
00:26:59,910 --> 00:27:00,790
Fine.

502
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:03,220
[Remember not to call him professor.]

503
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:04,800
[Call him Uncle He.]

504
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:06,510
[It sounds closer.]

505
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:07,470
[Understand?]

506
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,440
Yes.

507
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:09,750
I have other things to do.

508
00:27:09,840 --> 00:27:10,760
I'll hang up now.

509
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:26,800
How's that?

510
00:27:27,190 --> 00:27:28,070
Do I look good?

511
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:30,190
Well,

512
00:27:30,270 --> 00:27:31,630
it's the lady the one
celebrating her birthday.

513
00:27:31,710 --> 00:27:33,080
Why are you dressed so formal?

514
00:27:33,600 --> 00:27:35,590
This is the first birthday
I celebrate for her.

515
00:27:35,670 --> 00:27:37,560
And I should sing for her dormitory.

516
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:39,120
I must be well prepared.

517
00:27:39,950 --> 00:27:41,710
Don't keep a poker face when you sing.

518
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:42,470
Cheer up.

519
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:43,440
Wait...

520
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:44,700
Why should I sing?

521
00:27:44,790 --> 00:27:45,790
I... I'm not coming.

522
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:50,120
Li Qing Tong will also be there.

523
00:27:54,150 --> 00:27:55,030
Hurry up.

524
00:27:55,130 --> 00:27:57,100
I should also buy the cake, buddy.

525
00:27:58,960 --> 00:28:02,280
[Xin Tian Di Fun KTV]

526
00:28:02,280 --> 00:28:04,310
I shouldn't have had my hair cut.

527
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:05,360
Why not?

528
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:08,430
New haircut, three days of stupidity.

529
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:09,480
It's fine.

530
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:10,870
Don't eat too much later.

531
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:12,800
Treating us all is quite expensive.

532
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:14,240
Don't explain it to me.

533
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:16,070
It was her who was
always calling or texting me.

534
00:28:16,150 --> 00:28:16,990
I didn't even reply.

535
00:28:17,080 --> 00:28:18,140
How come she has your phone number?

536
00:28:18,230 --> 00:28:19,230
Who is he?

537
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:20,700
He's an older student.

538
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:21,750
Say hello to him.

539
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,750
You must be contacting
all girls in our college.

540
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:24,740
How could you say that?

541
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:25,550
Give me your phone.

542
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,520
I...

543
00:28:26,880 --> 00:28:27,630
What are you doing?

544
00:28:27,710 --> 00:28:28,670
You... Give it back to me.

545
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:29,790
Hello.

546
00:28:30,370 --> 00:28:31,250
Have a drink?

547
00:28:31,430 --> 00:28:32,320
No. Thanks.

548
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,510
Hello.

549
00:28:33,600 --> 00:28:35,190
This is my boyfriend Da Wang.

550
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,320
Hello.

551
00:28:37,460 --> 00:28:38,860
How about that? I'll pick a song for you.

552
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,320
No. Thanks.

553
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:43,430
Done.

554
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,720
I've deleted all the suspicious ones.

555
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,390
Zhang Wan Wan, you...

556
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:48,480
What?

557
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:50,560
You worked really hard.

558
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:53,550
Did I behave well?

559
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:54,840
Yeah.

560
00:28:55,520 --> 00:28:56,510
Come on, Xiao Shui. Sing a song.

561
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:57,480
Alright.

562
00:28:58,040 --> 00:28:58,920
Everybody's here.

563
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:01,190
Help yourselves.

564
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,230
Don't try to save money for me.

565
00:29:02,320 --> 00:29:03,230
That's great.

566
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:04,600
Told you not to eat too much.

567
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,280
I'm here.

568
00:29:10,240 --> 00:29:11,240
No online date today?

569
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:21,880
♫ Happy birthday to you ♫

570
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:26,280
♫ Happy birthday to you ♫

571
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,680
Blow the candles.

572
00:29:36,910 --> 00:29:38,200
What wish did you make?

573
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:42,070
I wish to receive your gifts every year.

574
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:43,760
You bet.

575
00:29:47,470 --> 00:29:48,640
Cut the cake.

576
00:29:51,810 --> 00:29:53,070
[Happy Birthday Li Jin Bu]

577
00:29:54,710 --> 00:29:55,480
[Xin Tian Di Fun KTV]

578
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:56,880
Ready... twenty.

579
00:29:57,050 --> 00:29:58,330
Ready... fifteen.

580
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:00,000
Ready... none.

581
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,110
You lost. Drink.

582
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:07,710
One more time.

583
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:09,680
Ready... ten.

584
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,500
Again.

585
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:20,320
Ready... five.

586
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:30,080
-How about changing to another game?
-No.

587
00:30:30,270 --> 00:30:31,320
I won't give in. Again.

588
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:40,800
Duan Xiao.

589
00:30:41,830 --> 00:30:43,680
May you be happy with Jin Bu.

590
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,790
Thanks. So may you.

591
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,120
Da Wang, drink with us.

592
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,600
Alright.

593
00:30:56,940 --> 00:30:57,640
You...

594
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:59,310
You won't come back during the break?

595
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,270
[I'm not sure either.]

596
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:02,270
[If I can go back,]

597
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:03,240
[I'll go back.]

598
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:07,000
Well, why don't you talk to your tutor?

599
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:08,870
I miss you.

600
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:10,720
[I'll try.]

601
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,390
If you don't come back,
I'll never talk to you.

602
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:14,680
[Li Qing Tong.]

603
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:16,400
[Could you stop being so childish?]

604
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:18,950
[You're not objective at all.]

605
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:20,430
[I have important things to do.]

606
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:23,000
[You'll give me too much pressure.]

607
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:24,720
[Why don't you put yourself my shoes?]

608
00:31:25,270 --> 00:31:26,150
I'm not...

609
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:28,960
What the...
So, I'm not understanding you again?

610
00:31:29,440 --> 00:31:31,640
How should I understand you?

611
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:35,800
It's you who contact me every
day as you please.

612
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:38,310
I just want to talk with you.

613
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,790
How come that gives you pressure?

614
00:31:40,790 --> 00:31:42,230
Is it my fault to miss you?

615
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:43,990
[Sorry.]

616
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:45,160
[It's my fault.]

617
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,480
[I shouldn't have said that.]

618
00:31:47,560 --> 00:31:48,710
You do this every time.

619
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,320
An apology,

620
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:53,320
and then do the same thing as before.

621
00:31:53,870 --> 00:31:55,270
[What on earth do you want me to do?]

622
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:57,000
[To quit college
to accompany you at home?]

623
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,280
Forget it.

624
00:32:04,670 --> 00:32:05,550
This conversation won't go anywhere.

625
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:07,000
Let it be.

626
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:22,030
[Just that mysterious man said,]

627
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:23,910
[days in college just go on slowly.]

628
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:27,110
Save some for me.

629
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:28,750
-Is it cooked yet?
-Yes.

630
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:35,080
Hello.

631
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:38,070
[People in love are still together.]

632
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,310
We're eating hotpot now.

633
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,790
[Day in and day out,]

634
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,550
[one semester after another,]

635
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:46,230
[nothing special has ever happened.]

636
00:32:46,320 --> 00:32:50,430
Go for it, go for it!

637
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:53,830
[Li Qing Tong is still trapped in
her difficult long-distance relationship.]

638
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:54,590
I'll go out right away.

639
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:56,550
[For her and Wu Zhi Xun,]

640
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:59,280
[the difference between their points
of view might be bigger]

641
00:32:59,390 --> 00:33:00,270
[that their distance.]

642
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:01,070
When will you come back?

643
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,030
[Let's stop here.]

644
00:33:02,120 --> 00:33:03,000
[I'll hang up.]

645
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,710
[But Li Qing Tong is
still confident about it.]

646
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:07,510
[Once she is determined about something,]

647
00:33:07,590 --> 00:33:08,840
[nobody can talk change into her.]

648
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,720
[On the contrary, I'm not.]

649
00:33:11,110 --> 00:33:13,950
[It seems that my relationship with
Duan Xiao is making everyone jealous.]

650
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:15,190
I did your laundry.

651
00:33:15,510 --> 00:33:16,740
[But in my inner heart,]

652
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:18,320
[there's no way for me to be determined.]

653
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:20,200
I'll do all the laundry
for you from today on.

654
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,990
[I've tried all my best
to treat him so well]

655
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:30,360
[that he even can't believe it.]

656
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:33,020
[So well that I feel I myself
have changed into another person.]

657
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:34,760
-Are you tired?
-Not really.

658
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:41,200
[The better I treat him,]

659
00:33:41,470 --> 00:33:42,590
[the sadder I feel.]

660
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:44,320
[Because only I know]

661
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:46,550
[there's no each other in our future.]

662
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:48,440
[Our story]

663
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:50,440
[is about to end.]

664
00:33:51,830 --> 00:33:53,260
There's only me in the dormitory.

665
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:54,910
They've all got internships outside.

666
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:56,600
[Why didn't you go?]

667
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,960
I'll go in the afternoon.

668
00:33:58,310 --> 00:33:59,750
Anything I can do for you?

669
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:01,310
No.

670
00:34:01,390 --> 00:34:02,640
Just mind your own business.

671
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,280
By the way,

672
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,460
how's the exchange-student program?

673
00:34:06,550 --> 00:34:07,840
[I didn't get the chance last time,]

674
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,350
but for this time,

675
00:34:09,429 --> 00:34:10,679
I think I can get it.

676
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:12,040
Wish you a good luck.

677
00:34:12,679 --> 00:34:13,870
[It's a pity]

678
00:34:13,949 --> 00:34:15,639
[that I'm never there
for your graduation.]

679
00:34:16,120 --> 00:34:17,000
[What a pity.]

680
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:18,960
[It's okay.]

681
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:21,360
[After graduating,
we'll be together forever.]

682
00:34:24,260 --> 00:34:27,719
[University Students Course Guidance]

683
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:28,719
Ms Ye.

684
00:34:29,110 --> 00:34:32,159
Can Li Qing Tong get another chance
to get an internship?

685
00:34:32,520 --> 00:34:34,239
Why are you always worrying about her?

686
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:35,710
Worry about yourself.

687
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,270
I don't care.

688
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,590
I'll go anyway.

689
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:40,480
I'll feel eased
if she's arranged before I go.

690
00:34:41,199 --> 00:34:42,360
Where are you going?

691
00:34:42,870 --> 00:34:43,750
I...

692
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,440
may study abroad.

693
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:47,150
It's worth celebrating.

694
00:34:47,239 --> 00:34:48,270
So,

695
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:50,469
could you please help Li Qing Tong
get a chance?

696
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:52,199
I'll try.

697
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:53,600
Thank you, Ms Ye.

698
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,880
When will you take the photos
for the graduation?

699
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:01,160
Tomorrow.

700
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:02,600
Okay.

701
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:03,760
I'll go there tomorrow.

702
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,000
So fast.

703
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,830
We're about to graduate.

704
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,150
I've made up my mind.

705
00:35:14,230 --> 00:35:15,280
When you graduate,

706
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,480
you can either stay here,

707
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,840
or go back to Tieyuan,

708
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,390
or go abroad.

709
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,310
When I graduate next year,

710
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,150
no matter where you are,

711
00:35:23,240 --> 00:35:24,350
I'll go there to find you.

712
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:30,800
Okay.

713
00:35:58,520 --> 00:36:00,760
I also want my boyfriend
to witness my graduation.

714
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:02,840
Look at the camera.

715
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:06,520
Three, two, one.

716
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:08,700
Okay, we'll take another one.

717
00:36:08,790 --> 00:36:09,830
Be more vivid.

718
00:36:09,910 --> 00:36:11,230
Do you think I'm vivid enough?

719
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:13,520
A little bit.

720
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,350
What's wrong with you?

721
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,310
He... He came back from Beijing.

722
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:31,440
Go now.

723
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:39,350
Why did you come here?

724
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,640
To give you a surprise.

725
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:43,840
Were you fooled by me?

726
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:49,360
I've never thought you could make it,

727
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:51,080
with such a bunch of flowers.

728
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,640
So unlike you.

729
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:54,320
If I hadn't come back,

730
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:56,360
I think she would have broken up with me.

731
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,600
A call from Professor He.

732
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:06,880
I need to take it.

733
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:14,840
Idiot.

734
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:17,230
I also considered buying flowers.

735
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:19,110
But then?

736
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,470
I came out so early

737
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:21,440
that the flower shop wasn't open yet.

738
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:24,670
I'll make it up for you tomorrow.

739
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:25,640
I promise they'll be
twice bigger than his.

740
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:26,750
No, I don't want them.

741
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,790
What a waste of money.

742
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:29,550
I'm not like Li Qing Tong.

743
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:30,920
I don't need such formalism.

744
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,800
Why did you arrive so late?

745
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:39,190
You should feel happy that I've come.

746
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,950
Always treating me as a third wheel?

747
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,230
Aren't you afraid
the car will flip around?

748
00:37:42,310 --> 00:37:43,360
Go away.

749
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:45,270
It's my boyfriend's seat.

750
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,150
What...

751
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:47,190
Where is he?

752
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:49,190
What? Is he afraid of meeting me?

753
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,760
Why should I?

754
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,360
Just kidding.

755
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:55,790
Get away.

756
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,600
Who's willing to sit next to you?

757
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:00,790
Give me the chopsticks.

758
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,350
Well... Eat now.

759
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:13,110
No leftover today.

760
00:38:17,950 --> 00:38:20,060
You have never seen
Chen Jun He taking care of kids.

761
00:38:20,150 --> 00:38:22,000
Wow. So brilliant.

762
00:38:22,590 --> 00:38:24,720
Are you sure he doesn't freak kids out?

763
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:26,910
What are you talking about?

764
00:38:26,990 --> 00:38:29,710
Let me tell you,
I'm an expert at comforting kids.

765
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,790
Kids follow me
as they don't want me to leave.

766
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,470
Because you freak them out?

767
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,750
Let me tell you,
you should be gentle to kids.

768
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:37,220
They're the flowers of our nation.

769
00:38:37,310 --> 00:38:39,110
Worry about yourself, okay?

770
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:41,480
You keep a poker face all the time
as if someone owed you money.

771
00:38:42,830 --> 00:38:45,710
Take me to a kindergarten next time.

772
00:38:45,790 --> 00:38:47,510
I think I'm good at
taking care of kids, too.

773
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:49,040
Just take care of yourself.

774
00:38:49,310 --> 00:38:50,830
Let me tell you, the naughty kids now,

775
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:52,600
you should treat them
with both candies and whips.

776
00:38:52,950 --> 00:38:54,150
You're just like an idiot girl,

777
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:55,030
and you'll be punched by kids.

778
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,670
Whom you're calling an idiot girl?

779
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:58,710
You... You're an idiot girl.

780
00:38:58,790 --> 00:39:00,750
I'm that kind of beautiful and...?

781
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,870
Cute girl.

782
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:05,390
Yes, I'm a beautiful and cute girl.

783
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,110
Have you forgotten last time
we took the bus?

784
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:08,510
That kid hit you.

785
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:10,310
-You were a mess.
-Who was to blame? You.

786
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,350
If you hadn't scolded him all the time,

787
00:39:12,430 --> 00:39:13,550
how could I have been hit?

788
00:39:13,630 --> 00:39:14,430
Look at you.

789
00:39:14,510 --> 00:39:15,710
Look at yourself in the mirror.

790
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:17,150
You... Stop talking about it.

791
00:39:17,240 --> 00:39:18,520
Let me tell you, I've made up my mind.

792
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:21,550
If I can't find a job,

793
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:23,870
I'll just go to a kindergarten
and be a teacher.

794
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,910
See? Even he can do this,

795
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:27,710
why can't I?

796
00:39:27,810 --> 00:39:29,870
-What did you say? Look at yourself.
-Li Qing Tong.

797
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:30,990
Eat while keeping quiet, okay?

798
00:39:31,080 --> 00:39:32,160
You're talking too much.

799
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:41,030
Why aren't you saying anything?

800
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:43,190
You were talking about your stuff,

801
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:44,640
I don't see how I can cut in.

802
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,430
I didn't see you eating either.

803
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:48,600
See how much food I've taken for you?

804
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,150
I'm full.

805
00:39:50,240 --> 00:39:51,120
Don't worry about me.

806
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:55,950
You said there's an event
after the meal, no?

807
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:57,280
At a KTV or something.

808
00:39:58,090 --> 00:39:58,910
Yeah.

809
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,150
I've booked a room.

810
00:40:00,240 --> 00:40:01,120
It's time to go.

811
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:02,990
Ask Zhang Wan Wan and the rest to join us.

812
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:04,070
Make it a graduation party.

813
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:05,040
Cheer up a bit.

814
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:06,310
Great.

815
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,160
Well, I won't go.

816
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:10,390
I have something else to do.

817
00:40:11,680 --> 00:40:12,680
I won't go, either.

818
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:14,320
I have an appointment with my classmates.

819
00:40:15,080 --> 00:40:17,430
I won't mess up with you lovers.

820
00:40:17,520 --> 00:40:18,390
Have fun.

821
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,360
I'm leaving.

822
00:40:23,150 --> 00:40:24,640
Can you go with us now?

823
00:40:25,120 --> 00:40:26,230
What do you mean?

824
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:27,390
I won't go

825
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:28,870
not because of him.

826
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:30,720
Do me a favour.

827
00:40:31,160 --> 00:40:33,000
Everybody's happy now.

828
00:40:34,210 --> 00:40:35,560
If you don't go, I won't, either.

829
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:37,230
It's not easy for you to come back.

830
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:38,630
Why don't you just have fun with us?

831
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:40,040
You can also take the chance
to accompany Li Qing Tong.

832
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,190
Let's go.

833
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,240
I'll pay the bill.

834
00:40:51,720 --> 00:40:52,600
Follow him.

835
00:40:56,540 --> 00:40:59,180
[Xin Tian Di Fun KTV]

836
00:41:06,120 --> 00:41:08,080
Men are all bad.

837
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,280
We...

838
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:12,280
We should keep changing them.

839
00:41:12,790 --> 00:41:14,720
You broke up with Fang Jin Han?

840
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,710
Before, a few times it was for joking.

841
00:41:20,590 --> 00:41:21,560
But this time,

842
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,600
we've really broken up.

843
00:41:34,670 --> 00:41:35,600
What?

844
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:40,480
I don't want to graduate.

845
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:43,710
Okay, okay.

846
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:44,790
We don't graduate.

847
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:46,230
We'll never graduate.

848
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,270
What happened?

849
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:50,070
What made you sad?

850
00:42:09,110 --> 00:42:09,990
Cheers.

851
00:42:23,070 --> 00:42:24,920
Don't be angry anymore.

852
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,870
I know I did something wrong today.

853
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:29,700
I promise I'll never do that again.

854
00:42:29,790 --> 00:42:31,520
Don't be angry.

855
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:37,180
Well, you...

856
00:42:37,270 --> 00:42:38,870
You shouldn't keep silent.

857
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:41,440
How can I understand you
if you don't talk?

858
00:42:42,440 --> 00:42:43,390
Tell me,

859
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:45,520
what should I do to comfort you?

860
00:42:53,400 --> 00:42:54,360
I know.

861
00:42:55,200 --> 00:42:56,800
You have no deep affection on me.

862
00:43:54,120 --> 00:43:55,000
Good morning.

863
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:56,920
Good morning.

864
00:44:00,990 --> 00:44:01,870
Qing Tong.

865
00:44:03,430 --> 00:44:05,160
Come to Beijing with me.

866
00:44:08,080 --> 00:44:09,120
Okay.

867
00:44:26,080 --> 00:44:26,870
How do you feel?

868
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:27,840
Do you still feel sick?

869
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:29,070
My head still aches a bit.

870
00:44:30,390 --> 00:44:31,590
Don't drink too much next time.

871
00:44:33,440 --> 00:44:34,320
Here you are.

872
00:44:35,230 --> 00:44:36,110
What is it?

873
00:44:36,550 --> 00:44:37,670
A graduation gift for you.

874
00:44:37,750 --> 00:44:38,550
It's just the first one.

875
00:44:38,630 --> 00:44:39,550
There are still more gifts coming.

876
00:44:39,630 --> 00:44:40,590
Don't unwrap it.

877
00:44:40,680 --> 00:44:42,030
Unwrap it later.

878
00:44:43,590 --> 00:44:44,470
Let's go.

879
00:44:58,960 --> 00:44:59,960
Idiot.

880
00:45:00,480 --> 00:45:02,240
Don't you know
I don't like wearing skirts?

881
00:45:05,150 --> 00:45:06,400
[I didn't lie to him.]

882
00:45:06,840 --> 00:45:08,400
[I really don't want to graduate.]

883
00:45:09,200 --> 00:45:10,390
[I hope]

884
00:45:10,480 --> 00:45:12,160
[to stay with him like this]

885
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:13,950
[forever.]

886
00:45:23,240 --> 00:45:24,670
Why are you laughing?

887
00:45:24,760 --> 00:45:26,680
I feel so happy for your big day.

888
00:45:27,030 --> 00:45:28,630
It's just an anniversary.

889
00:45:28,720 --> 00:45:30,070
You make it as if it were my wedding.

890
00:45:30,160 --> 00:45:31,360
No way.

891
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:32,680
Oh, I almost forgot.

892
00:45:33,190 --> 00:45:34,790
There is a bracelet
I've treasured for a long time,

893
00:45:34,880 --> 00:45:36,350
I've never worn it myself.

894
00:45:36,440 --> 00:45:37,640
I'll lend it to you.

895
00:45:44,080 --> 00:45:46,000
I'll lend you my pink skirt.

896
00:45:46,160 --> 00:45:47,390
I don't want to wear skirts.

897
00:45:48,150 --> 00:45:49,800
Are you sure you're going to wear these?

898
00:46:06,040 --> 00:46:07,240
A date again?

899
00:46:08,120 --> 00:46:09,560
For what excuse this time?

900
00:46:10,710 --> 00:46:11,710
None of your business.

901
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,470
I'll tell you when you get a girlfriend.

902
00:46:16,670 --> 00:46:17,470
He's talking about you.

903
00:46:17,550 --> 00:46:18,800
I don't need any girlfriend.

904
00:46:36,960 --> 00:46:38,310
We're almost at the station.

905
00:46:38,400 --> 00:46:40,080
Be ready to get off the bus.

906
00:46:40,310 --> 00:46:42,390
The end will come sooner or later.

907
00:47:08,620 --> 00:47:16,670
[Lin Yang Technology University]

908
00:47:29,080 --> 00:47:31,200
Duan Xiao.

909
00:47:33,480 --> 00:47:34,550
Duan Xiao.
